  "body": "## Gig Search Report — March 10, 2026\n\nSearched X.com and Contra.com across all 6 target categories. Here are the strongest leads found.\n\n---\n\n### [Figma Design] Freelance UI/UX Designer — Mobile App\n- **Platform**: X.com\n- **URL**: https://x.com/Yashank18/status/1963555763508711469\n- **Posted**: Recent (2026)\n- **Budget**: Not specified\n- **Notes**: Looking for freelance UI/UX designer for mobile app UI (iOS/Android) in Figma. Remote. Wants sleek visual taste, micro-interactions & lightweight design systems. Direct DM to apply. **Strong lead — clear requirements, remote, ongoing potential.**\n\n### [Rive Design] Motion Designer & Character Animator — Rilla\n- **Platform**: X.com (via @rive_app)\n- **URL**: https://x.com/rive_app/status/1981068687726825927\n- **Posted**: Recent (2026)\n- **Budget**: $60–$100/hr (Contract-to-Hire)\n- **Notes**: NYC-based, posted by Rive's official account. Motion designer and character animator role. **High-quality lead — clear budget, good rate, contract-to-hire path.**\n\n### [Fullstack] Junior Fullstack Developer — HackerNoon\n- **Platform**: X.com\n- **URL**: https://x.com/job_openings_ng/status/1975095322880901488\n- **Posted**: Recent (2026)\n- **Budget**: $500–$1,000/mo trial; $2,000–$3,000/mo full-time\n- **Notes**: Remote (Asia/Africa). 70% backend (Node.js, Express, MongoDB), 30% frontend (Next.js, React). Entry-level, could be stepping stone.\n\n### [Fullstack] Middle+ Full-Stack Developer (React + Node.js)\n- **Platform**: X.com\n- **URL**: https://x.com/tohire_ng/status/2000176713007771791\n- **Posted**: Recent (2026)\n- **Budget**: Not specified\n- **Notes**: E-commerce startup building Telegram MiniApp. React + Vite + Tailwind + Redux Toolkit frontend, Node + Express + Mongo backend. Full-time role with growth potential to senior.\n\n### [Fullstack] Staff Web Engineer — Fueled\n- **Platform**: X.com (via @Javascriptjobbs)\n- **URL**: https://x.com/Javascriptjobbs/status/1954635363021914575\n- **Posted**: Recent (2026)\n- **Budget**: Not specified\n- **Notes**: Remote worldwide. Fueled is a well-known digital product agency. JavaScript, React, Node.js, Vue.js stack.\n\n### [Fullstack] React Developer — Tree Ring Digital\n- **Platform**: X.com (via @Javascriptjobbs)\n- **URL**: https://x.com/Javascriptjobbs/status/1952067948106973594\n- **Posted**: Recent (2026)\n- **Budget**: Not specified\n- **Notes**: Remote, United States.\n\n### [Fullstack] Frontend Engineer Intern — SafeDep\n- **Platform**: X.com\n- **URL**: https://x.com/safedepio/status/2008795693604090315\n- **Posted**: Recent (2026)\n- **Budget**: Paid internship\n- **Notes**: TypeScript + Next.js, building interfaces from Figma designs. Remote. Mentorship from founding engineers. Good for junior candidates.\n\n### [Fullstack] Next.js Team — Web Performance Engineer\n- **Platform**: X.com\n- **URL**: https://x.com/feedthejim/status/1994431099448258581\n- **Posted**: Recent (2026)\n- **Budget**: Not specified\n- **Notes**: Jimmy Lai (Next.js team lead at Vercel) looking for someone obsessed with web performance. Strong React skills required. **Premium opportunity — working on Next.js itself.**\n\n### [Figma Design] Product Designer, Cross-Product Foundations — Figma\n- **Platform**: X.com (via @wlpjobs)\n- **URL**: https://x.com/wlpjobs/status/1955184731215081886\n- **Posted**: Recent (2026)\n- **Budget**: Not specified (Figma-level compensation)\n- **Notes**: Remote US. Full-time role at Figma itself.\n\n### [Figma Design] Product Designer, Developer Tools — Figma\n- **Platform**: X.com (via @wlpjobs)\n- **URL**: https://x.com/wlpjobs/status/1974096596385067139\n- **Posted**: Recent (2026)\n- **Budget**: Not specified (Figma-level compensation)\n- **Notes**: London, UK. Full-time role at Figma.\n\n---\n\n## Contra.com Leads\n\n### [Figma/Framer] Website Redesign and Design Project Assistance\n- **Platform**: Contra.com\n- **URL**: https://contra.com/featured-jobs/freelance-ux-jobs\n- **Posted**: Listed on Contra jobs board\n- **Budget**: Not specified\n- **Notes**: Lead website redesign. Proficiency with Framer and Webflow is a plus. Contractor, remote.\n\n### [Figma Design] BIDZ — Quick Figma Redesign Brief\n- **Platform**: Contra.com\n- **URL**: https://contra.com/featured-jobs/freelance-ux-jobs\n- **Posted**: Listed on Contra jobs board\n- **Budget**: Not specified\n- **Notes**: Figma redesign project. Contractor, remote.\n\n### [Spline/3D] 3D Web Developer — Pokémon Pack Opening\n- **Platform**: Contra.com\n- **URL**: https://contra.com/featured-jobs/freelance-web-developer-jobs\n- **Posted**: Listed on Contra jobs board\n- **Budget**: Not specified\n- **Notes**: Create interactive 3D virtual experience using Three.js/WebGL. Contract, remote. **Relevant for Spline/3D skills — similar tech stack.**\n\n### [Animation] Interactive Progress Bar Animator for Learning Platform\n- **Platform**: Contra.com\n- **URL**: https://contra.com/featured-jobs/freelance-ux-jobs\n- **Posted**: Listed on Contra jobs board\n- **Budget**: Not specified\n- **Notes**: Interactive progress bar with responsive design and animations. Contractor, remote. **Good fit for Rive animation skills.**\n\n---\n\n## Key Accounts to Follow for Ongoing Leads\n\n| Account | Platform | Category |\n|---------|----------|----------|\n| [@framerjobs](https://x.com/framerjobs) | X.com | Framer jobs board |\n| [@Javascriptjobbs](https://x.com/Javascriptjobbs) | X.com | JS/React/Node jobs |\n| [@react_jobs](https://x.com/react_jobs) | X.com | React jobs |\n| [@nextjs_jobs](https://twitter.com/nextjs_jobs) | X.com | Next.js jobs |\n| [@fullstackjob](https://x.com/fullstackjob) | X.com | Fullstack dev jobs |\n| [@wlpjobs](https://x.com/wlpjobs) | X.com | Product & design jobs |\n| [@rive_app](https://x.com/rive_app) | X.com | Rive animation |\n| [@animationjobs](https://x.com/animationjobs) | X.com | Animation jobs |\n\n## Summary\n\n- **14 leads** found across X.com and Contra.com\n- **Top 3 leads**: Rive